snippet.title: Pixelborn - first PvP test stream (The Card Game Simulator)
snippet.description:
Now that we know the game's rules, we didn't waste time and updated the engine so it is time to play some PvP games. 

All rights reserved to Disney and Ravensburger. I do not own any of the images used to create this sample.

If you want to follow the development progress, you can join our Disord server: https://discord.gg/qBBQ2D384A
